comments: Randle (NYK) cleanly deflects the ball from Simons (POR).
Robinson (NYK) sets the screen on Simons (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Simons (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Quickley (NYK).
Robinson (NYK) and Kanter (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Quickley (NYK) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Replay review of the foul called on Simons (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Simons makes contact with Quickley (NYK) while he is in the act of shooting.
Kanter (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Randle (NYK) during the drive.
Trent Jr. (POR) and Robinson (NYK) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Kanter (POR) establishes a legal guarding position in Randle's (NYK) path and makes contact with the ball to force a tie-up.
Burks (NYK) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) arm and affects his SQBR.
Randle (NYK) cleanly dislodges the ball from Anthony (POR).
Randle (NYK) makes contact with Anthony's (POR) arm and affects his SQBR.
Anthony (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Randle (NYK).
Randle (NYK) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Jones Jr. (POR) makes marginal contact with Quickley (NYK) at the start of his drive.
Randle (NYK) commits a take foul on Anthony (POR).
Randle (NYK) makes contact with Covington's (POR) head during the free throw. After communicating with the Replay Center it was determined this did not meet the criteria of a flagrant foul.
Jones Jr. (POR) makes contact with Quickley's (NYK) arm during the horizontal motion of his rip-through. A personal foul, not a shooting foul, should have been called.
Covington (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Quickley (NYK) during the drive.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
